      "raw_text": "p. J. Graham and Tom Stein\nbach. union machinists, arrested in\nconnection with the Union Iron\nworks strike for the alleged assault\nIng of one of tho strikebreakers and\nafterward released, has concluded\nto bring civil action for malicious\narrest against J. M. Fitzpatrick,\nmanager of the iron plant.\n\n\nr. D. Wyant. arrested on a sim\nliar charge. will bring a separate\nspit. The men propose to see If the\ncourts afford any protection against\narrest on alleged trumpet charges\nIn labor disputes."
